    <item>
      <title>Prompting</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/tech/knowledge-base/ai/prompting/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/tech/knowledge-base/ai/prompting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Prompting is the primary interface for directing language model behaviour. The quality of the prompt determines the quality of the output.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;be-specific&#34;&gt;Be Specific&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Vague prompts produce vague responses. State the format, length, audience, and constraints explicitly.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Vague&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Specific&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&amp;ldquo;Write a summary&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&amp;ldquo;Summarise in 3 bullet points for a non-technical audience&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&amp;ldquo;Improve this code&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&amp;ldquo;Refactor this Python function for readability; no logic changes&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&amp;ldquo;Write a blog post&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&amp;ldquo;Write a 500-word post for senior engineers on X, technical tone, no intro fluff&amp;rdquo;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The model will fill gaps in your prompt with its default assumptions. If the defaults don&amp;rsquo;t match what you want, specify explicitly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
